        <ul>
            <li><strong><u>10.1 Disclaimer of Warranties. </u></strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>(a) YOUR USE OF THE SERVICES IS “AS IS” AND AT YOUR SOLE RISK, AND WYTH MAKES NO REPRESENTATIONS OR WARRANTIES, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, AS TO THE NATURE, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, RELIABILITY, TIMELINESS, COMPLETENESS, MERCHANTABILITY, NON-INFRINGEMENT OR SAFETY OF THE SERVICES OR ANYTHING IN CONNECTION WITH THE SERVICES (INCLUDING THE CONDUCT OF ITS USERS, THE CONTENT SUPPLIED BY ITS USERS, OR IN CONNECTION WITH ANY CARPOOL TRIP OR CONFIRMED TRIP).</li>
                    <li>(b) WYTH MAKES NO REPRESENTATIONS OR WARRANTIES, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, AS TO THE COVERAGE, APPLICABILITY, VALIDITY, OR SUFFICIENCY OF THE REQUIRED INSURANCE OR ITS COVERAGE FOR ANY LOSS, DAMAGE, COST OR EXPENSE INCURRED BY YOU IN CONNECTION WITH THE SERVICES. </li>
