                <ul>
                    <li>(a) WYTH DISCLAIMS LIABILITY FOR ANY AND ALL LOSSES, DAMAGE, COST, OR EXPENSES INCURRED OR SUSTAINED BY, OR IMPOSED BY, ARISING OUT OF, WITH RESPECT TO, OR BY REASON OF YOUR CRIMINAL, WILLFUL, OR GROSSLY NEGLIGENT ACTION OR OMISSION IN CONNECTION WITH THE SERVICES. </li>
